# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:13
translate chinese jezq2_7e645245:

    # det "What are you going to do if we find your dad?"
    det "如果我们找到了你爸爸，你会怎么做？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:14
translate chinese jezq2_b55c740c:

    # pc "I'm going to hug him. Tell him I'm sorry for the things that I said and did."
    pc "我会抱抱他。告诉他，为我曾经说的话和做的事向他道歉。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:15
translate chinese jezq2_ab3ff14b:

    # pc "Tell him I love him."
    pc "告诉他，我爱他。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:17
translate chinese jezq2_2e7485fd:

    # det "That's nice."
    det "真好。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:18
translate chinese jezq2_070ecc32:

    # pc "Then I guess I'll just keep on like I have been. Except I'll try to spend more time with him."
    pc "那我大概会像以前一样继续生活。不过我会尽量多陪陪他。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:19
translate chinese jezq2_84c06b07:

    # pc "I have a lot of questions for him."
    pc "我有好多问题想问他。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:21
translate chinese jezq2_c85babbc:

    # det "And what if we find him, but he's... um..."
    det "如果我们找到他，但他……呃……"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:22
translate chinese jezq2_64d707d2:

    # pc "Not alive?"
    pc "已经不在人世了呢？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:23
translate chinese jezq2_efaf6eb5:

    # det "Yeah."
    det "是啊。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:25
translate chinese jezq2_820bd703:

    # det "You don't have to answer that. I shouldn't have asked."
    det "你不用回答。我不该问的。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:26
translate chinese jezq2_2e4c59d4:

    # det "What a downer. I'm so bad at normal conversation."
    det "真扫兴。我真不擅长正常聊天。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:28
translate chinese jezq2_b219d344:

    # pc "It's okay."
    pc "没关系。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:29
translate chinese jezq2_69298cee:

    # pc "If Dad's not alive, I would be sad, of course."
    pc "如果爸爸不在人世，我当然会很难过。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:30
translate chinese jezq2_ec2c3b68:

    # pc "I'd have a lot of regrets that I would have to live with."
    pc "我会带着许多遗憾度过余生。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:32
translate chinese jezq2_068843ff:

    # pc "I would just hope that somehow he'd know that I love him and I appreciate everything that he's done for me."
    pc "我只希望他能以某种方式知道，我爱他，也感激他为我所做的一切。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:33
translate chinese jezq2_661a213e:

    # pc "And I'd try to live up to his expectations."
    pc "我会努力不辜负他的期望。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:35
translate chinese jezq2_29d642c1:

    # det "I'm sure that wherever he is, he knows how you feel."
    det "我相信，无论他在哪里，他都知道你的心意。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:36
translate chinese jezq2_31173ab5:

    # det "But I really hope that you get a chance to tell him."
    det "但我真的希望你能有机会亲口告诉他。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/JezConversation/jezq2.rpy:37
translate chinese jezq2_1f8cc682:

    # pc "Thanks, Jez. So do I."
    pc "谢谢，杰兹。我也是。"

